'''頭胸部'''（'''cephalothorax'''）是許多[[節肢動物|節肢動物]]的一個[[體段|體段]]，包括相連的[[頭部|頭部]]和[[胸部|胸部]]，與[[腹部|腹部]]截然相別。<ref name="Biology">{{cite book |author=Eldra Pearl Solomon, Linda R. Berg & Diana W. Martin |year=2004 |title=Biology |edition=7th |publisher=Cengage Learning |isbn=978-0-534-49276-2 |chapter=Tha animal kingdom: an introduction to animal diversity |pages=534–549 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=UCUxpgfcoNsC&pg=PA573 |access-date=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104153043/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=UCUxpgfcoNsC&pg=PA573 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 術語"cephalothorax"一詞來自[[希臘語|希臘語]]{{lang|el|[[:wikt:κεφαλή|κεφαλή]]}}（頭部，{{lang|el|kephalé}}）和{{lang|el|θώραξ}}（胸部，{{lang|el|[[:wikt:thorax|thórax]]}}）。<ref>{{cite book |author=Timothy J. Gibb & C. Y. Oseto |year=2006 |title=Arthropod Collection and Identification: Field and Laboratory Techniques |publisher=[[Academic_Press|Academic Press]] |isbn=978-0-12-369545-1 |chapter=Glossary |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qwO-9ElVPlMC&pg=PT180 |access-date=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2020-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200611233551/https://books.google.co.uk/books?id=qwO-9ElVPlMC&pg=PT180&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref> 最常見於[[螯肢亞門|螯肢亞門]]和[[甲殼亞門|甲殼亞門]]的生物身上，在其他諸如[[六足亞門|六足亞門]]生物身上頭胸依舊是分離的。<ref name="Biology"/> [[鲎|鲎]]和許多甲殼亞門動物的頭胸部都有[[甲殼|甲殼]]覆蓋。<ref>{{cite book |author=Andrew J. Martinez |year=2003 |title=Marine Life of the North Atlantic: Canada to New England |edition=3rd |publisher=Aqua Quest Publications |isbn=978-1-881652-32-8 |chapter=Arthropoda (crabs, shrimps, lobsters) |pages=144–175 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dq-iIBVn4_MC&pg=PA144 |access-date=2013-12-07 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104153138/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=dq-iIBVn4_MC&pg=PA144 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

